opic period. Moreover, we show that our new as\nwell as previous photometry does not contain evidence for the quoted\nphotometric period.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Aug 2016 14:44:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-26"}
